msg: Add a "clean.runtime" target to the NetUI build.xml file.  Cleaning "coreWeb" from the build.xml/clean target messes up a common scenario of how DRTs can be run.
No reason to have to rebuild the entire DRT app every time a "clean deploy" is done for the runtime.
